# 10. Validation Checklist

Before committing:

- [ ] `make gen` executed after any relevant change
- [ ] `make gen-check` passes
- [ ] no manual edits to generated files exist
- [ ] CI codegen checks satisfied
- [ ] annotations and `part` directives correct
- [ ] preflight passes